==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water nymph
<hw>Wa"ter nymph`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Myth.)</fld>
<def>A goddess of any stream or other body of water, whether one of the
Naiads, Nereids, or Oceanides.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A water lily
(<gen>Nymphaea</gen>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water oat</ent>⟦br⟧
